{
  "stem": "14060.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just would like to go back in the period of-- in-- of 1940, '41 period when, I think I mentioned earlier-- and please correct me if I said the story-- when we had to prove our Hungarian nationality.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, there were Jews who escaped from Austria-- unfortunately for them, in the wrong direction-- to Hungary from Czechoslovakia, and also in 1940 from Poland.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many of them tried to get Aryan papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Others they k-- like Polish soldiers because there was a friendship treaty, so to speak, between Hungary and Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were in some difficulty, the Hungarians, at that point, when the Germans marched into Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But nevertheless, a lot of Jews also came over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, obviously, the police in the Hungarian government-- because you had the-- a reporting duty that anybody who lived in any house had to be reported within 24 hours that he's living there-- got to know that a lot of Jews have come in, particularly from Poland and also from these other two countries.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And therefore, the Hungarian government made a special effort to pursue the policy of proving your nationality.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had no problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We'd proven it, in fact, back up to 1820 when the records started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I'm not talking of personal problems.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But what happened was that anybody else who they caught who could not prove it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they have records, they knew where people lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because up to that point, people were not worried about that they're going to do anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They caught them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They interned them in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in due course, they deported them to Kamianets-Podilskyi, is the place called in Poland where they were, in 1942, shot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We found it out at the later stage.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
